These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Cigar: siglo, chaman, prince, pall-mall
Hobby: board-games, gardening, hiking, sudoku
1. Cigar:chaman is between Cigar:siglo and Hobby:gardening##2
2. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Hobby:board-games##3
3. Cigar:chaman is somewhere between Cigar:pall-mall and Cigar:siglo##7
4. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
5. Cigar:pall-mall is on the right of Hobby:hiking##1
6. Hobby:gardening is somewhere to the left of Hobby:board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | prince | pall-mall       | chaman | siglo        |
| Hobby      | hiking  | gardening | sudoku        | board-games |

