.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Movie-Genre: musical, epic, western, action
Sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. Movie-Genre:musical is somewhere between Sport:golf and Movie-Genre:action##7
3. Movie-Genre:western == Sport:volleyball##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
5. Movie-Genre:epic is on the left of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | musical | action       | western |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

